Mounting Procedure 
==================

|Product| supports VESA 100 x 100 mounting pattern with 4 x M4 screws, enabling simplified installation onto any standard VESA mounting rack (:ref:`guide <vesa_mguide>`). 

You can also mount |product| with panel mounting method (:ref:`guide <panel_mguide>`).

You can find detailed information about mounting in the |mguide|.